39:50.346 --> 39:53.432
and her success as a chef.

39:53.516 --> 39:56.310
Which is an amazing, beautiful surprise.

40:00.481 --> 40:03.109
<i>We are very proud.</i>

40:03.192 --> 40:08.614
<i>Proud of all she has</i>
<i>accomplished not only at home...</i>

40:08.697 --> 40:12.535
